@Strudel Dad

My favorite language-based pet peeve is when people of my generation regurgitate, fifty-some years later, what their middle and high school English teachers  taught them was correct, despite the fact that most of those recommendations were made because the language was already changing then. 

(Almost nobody pronounces the first R in February anymore. Just wait until shows debuting then are advertised on TV later this year.)

@Heidi

Hey like I, totally got it on the crosses, fer sere. 

