@HeathieJ

Maybe it’s just my allegiance to Blondie and Talking Heads, but  I thought  CBGB was on par with venues like Madison Square Garden or Wembley Stadium.  It closed about 20 years ago, and now I learn it’s the address of some sketchy menswear designer. Whatever. It’s still the punk rock home of my dreams.

Hoorah! It applies.

@Heidi 

