I think this one counts.

@Helen Wright
One doesn't even have to have resd classical literature to know ROUE. Every duke or earl in romance fiction set in a certain time starts out as a ROUE before meeting the woman who tames him. :)  

IONE Skye was in a very popular 1989 movie called Say Anything, which also starred John Cusack and John Mahoney (who went on to become Frasier's dad on tv). You may also know she was Donovan's daughter.

